Salami Label design

Project Description:

This was a label design project for International Gold Star, Inc. The requirement was to create a label that would have a lot of gold in it and the theme would be old russian traditions. The new line was named "Russian crown", so it was recommended to use images of a crown and a two headed eagle.

Used technologies:

I used Adobe Illustrator to create and edit the design.
